# Flight Status and Notifications

## Description
This project provides real-time flight status updates and notifications to passengers.

## Features
- Real-time flight status updates (delays, cancellations, gate changes)
- Push notifications for flight status changes via Kafka
- Email notifications for flight status changes
- Integration with mock airport data

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: React.js
- Backend: Flask (Python)
- Database: MongoDB
- Notifications: Kafka, SMTP

## Setup
1. Clone the repository
2. Install dependencies for the backend and frontend
3. Run MongoDB and Kafka
4. Start the backend and frontend servers

## Additional Tools/Libraries
- Axios for API requests in React
- Confluent Kafka Python client for Kafka integration in Flask
- smtplib for email notifications
